{"tid":371881,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手收音問題","createTime":"2017-08-24T03:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T01:23:30.000Z","uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61baabbf5b2702b90b1a5a8cde89da59c4f99cf6","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"利申左先，極新手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家target諗緊買 canon m6 / sony a5100 拍vlog用既<br />\n<br />\n貪有得反mon自拍<br />\n<br />\n想問下收音個方面想收清楚兩三米外我講緊野既聲，冇雜音係咪用無線領夾咪會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再問無線領夾咪係咪要有hot shoe 或者 Bluetooth 黎博？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為a5100好似兩樣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n褲已除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手睇相機，原來咁複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n配件好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f1ba8647ba860f5adf8b75963fb32781518aca","tid":371881,"uid":14875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"想再簡單啲可以試下用有咪嘅耳機錄之後再sync聲"},{"pid":"22efe0adbc5f177418c80911d89f0771fbdfa434","tid":371881,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones/ecm-aw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com.hk%2Fzh%2Felectronics%2Finterchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones%2Fecm-aw4&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1c5c5e8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones/ecm-aw4</a>"},{"pid":"6f17962087c5e3b741b93a371d5ca3b318f86bd3","tid":371881,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"如果你想睇你片既人睇得舒服就唔好用部相機收音"},{"pid":"a742d8f78f779dfe512b32df580ec6242525006d","tid":371881,"uid":128320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"用緊a5100，想知有冇得拍片同時影埋相？"},{"pid":"bb7eee4e4ec88dcbe1787380b00d0f46fa8459e1","tid":371881,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"用外置咪？"},{"pid":"00fefb2efe80cb7f0e2dce1376d5db57a46ec1bc","tid":371881,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"買呢類cage<br />\n再買個螺絲冷靴駁無線receiver<br />\n無線咪買Azden 已經夠用<br />\n有款一千鬆啲有交易<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/135402_f2d5a727bd9fb1fc8e56a2c8841197ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F135402_f2d5a727bd9fb1fc8e56a2c8841197ff.jpg&h=7911a7ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1533cf87d3a5f574035f04466df125ec9713102c","tid":371881,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"用iPhone錄再sync返"},{"pid":"fb620a0e341676c325a014c44d9f6af4453bdd71","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones/ecm-aw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com.hk%2Fzh%2Felectronics%2Finterchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones%2Fecm-aw4&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1c5c5e8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras-microphones/ecm-aw4</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢支會唔會同啲鏡一樣要跟返廠先用到架？<br />\n<br />\n有bluetooth就用到？ 有睇過呢啲，但a5100好似用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d973302cb7f21a0cbf6e6cfd0a9f3611bf91e0ee","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你想睇你片既人睇得舒服就唔好用部相機收音</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白，所以先問收音點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7049c38712b6d68cbeaa5c46fcad219e9f1d8c2","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用iPhone錄再sync返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好易出現聲畫唔同步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係要好似拍戲咁打板會易啲"},{"pid":"5597c4fff6aa94cc9321a1a1fffcbf8b0de59b7f","tid":371881,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用iPhone錄再sync返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好易出現聲畫唔同步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係要好似拍戲咁打板會易啲</blockquote><br />\n無板咪拍手 拍個下就sync到"},{"pid":"2e7eeeea2370ef940f929e8400b8c096d7491a88","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用iPhone錄再sync返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會好易出現聲畫唔同步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係要好似拍戲咁打板會易啲</blockquote><br />\n無板咪拍手 拍個下就sync到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但既然都係買機又盛既話都想知埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f099cc3da9115a9d2111d99f704111daf8044eb","tid":371881,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"收音一字既之曰「近」<br />\n如果又要對白又要環境聲，分開收音方便後制。"},{"pid":"09e2bf186f5cb6c77a4d1c2a9e3b5552a5bdff37","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收音一字既之曰「近」<br />\n如果又要對白又要環境聲，分開收音方便後制。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係收我講野既聲，至於環境聲就唔想有，最多係可能多個人講野遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以先睇到話外置買領帶夾<br />\n<br />\n至於後制聲個方面你地講既係分開錄完剪返落去定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果係既就可免則免<br />\n<br />\n最想問都係部機係咪要有hot shoe 或者bluetooth先support 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而內置個個咪係咪完全唔洗指意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋自己有個藍芽耳機聽開歌，用黎收又work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a9ba86fe233f234d7d02968a0b02ff4cd5277d","tid":371881,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"a51000 無3.5mm mic 插頭<br />\n原廠熱靴收音set又唔support<br />\n<a href=\"http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.d-imaging.sony.co.jp%2Fwww%2Fcscs%2Faccessories%2Fcompatibility.php%3Farea%3Dgb%26lang%3Dct%26mdl%3DXLR-K2M%26cat%3D3%26loc%3Dzh_HK&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=85186f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK</a><br />\n收嚟真係把撚"},{"pid":"733311838e7a30aed4568d755df494223f131a51","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a51000 無3.5mm mic 插頭<br />\n原廠熱靴收音set又唔support<br />\n<a href=\"http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.d-imaging.sony.co.jp%2Fwww%2Fcscs%2Faccessories%2Fcompatibility.php%3Farea%3Dgb%26lang%3Dct%26mdl%3DXLR-K2M%26cat%3D3%26loc%3Dzh_HK&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=85186f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK</a><br />\n收嚟真係把撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，我就係睇到a5100好似又冇bluetooth 又冇hot shoe 乜都唔support先問下，買錯冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇啲色鍾意sony啲先考慮佢，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d3ae366ab9ea06d62c0ea7446fc80f4e7dfa0b","tid":371881,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>a51000 無3.5mm mic 插頭<br />\n原廠熱靴收音set又唔support<br />\n<a href=\"http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.d-imaging.sony.co.jp%2Fwww%2Fcscs%2Faccessories%2Fcompatibility.php%3Farea%3Dgb%26lang%3Dct%26mdl%3DXLR-K2M%26cat%3D3%26loc%3Dzh_HK&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=85186f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK</a><br />\n收嚟真係把撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，我就係睇到a5100好似又冇bluetooth 又冇hot shoe 乜都唔support先問下，買錯冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇啲色鍾意sony啲先考慮佢，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上6500"},{"pid":"96360f9537f300ec164bfaa8630793b74d7b9f38","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a51000 無3.5mm mic 插頭<br />\n原廠熱靴收音set又唔support<br />\n<a href=\"http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.d-imaging.sony.co.jp%2Fwww%2Fcscs%2Faccessories%2Fcompatibility.php%3Farea%3Dgb%26lang%3Dct%26mdl%3DXLR-K2M%26cat%3D3%26loc%3Dzh_HK&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=85186f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://support.d-imaging.sony.co.jp/www/cscs/accessories/compatibility.php?area=gb&amp;lang=ct&amp;mdl=XLR-K2M&amp;cat=3&amp;loc=zh_HK</a><br />\n收嚟真係把撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，我就係睇到a5100好似又冇bluetooth 又冇hot shoe 乜都唔support先問下，買錯冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇啲色鍾意sony啲先考慮佢，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上6500</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想要有flip out mon 自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3835a21de963bc4a35c5c2ad8b299c20b6be367e","tid":371881,"uid":3858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EHNqK3CGkT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEHNqK3CGkT8&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79af1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b5cbe03d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EHNqK3CGkT8</a>"},{"pid":"cfdc718f105b50a9953de577949f65fc5584c804","tid":371881,"uid":36554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"一係買支gun, indoor買支pencil type既condenser都可以<br />\neg. rode ntg1, AKG c1000s etc.<br />\n好處係可以收幾個人講野同時唔太大ambiance<br />\n係咁意落個denoise都ok<br />\n壞處係outdoor好嘈既話ambiance都係會大 除非你拎著黎講<br />\n<br />\n一係買set wireless belt pack<br />\neg. sennheiser EW100, Shure SLX<br />\n好似買返黎有跟支mic<br />\n有錢想換咪可以諗<br />\ncountryman b3, Dpa 4060 etc.<br />\n鴨記咪霸mic pro係窮撚最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n好處係正確戴mic 冇jam到野同唔係蚊之咁細聲既話<br />\n無論indoor定outdoor都係收得最清楚<br />\n壞處係你有3個人講野你就要3set<br />\n<br />\n記著<br />\n無論用咩mic 你唔夠聲然後俾勁大mic gain都係會好大ambiance<br />\n記得拍板／手 <br />\n<br />\n利申: Audio佬 唔識相機野"},{"pid":"906a8cc2251d65e38d2423e348395c886ba3a9d2","tid":371881,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係買支gun, indoor買支pencil type既condenser都可以<br />\neg. rode ntg1, AKG c1000s etc.<br />\n好處係可以收幾個人講野同時唔太大ambiance<br />\n係咁意落個denoise都ok<br />\n壞處係outdoor好嘈既話ambiance都係會大 除非你拎著黎講<br />\n<br />\n一係買set wireless belt pack<br />\neg. sennheiser EW100, Shure SLX<br />\n好似買返黎有跟支mic<br />\n有錢想換咪可以諗<br />\ncountryman b3, Dpa 4060 etc.<br />\n鴨記咪霸mic pro係窮撚最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n好處係正確戴mic 冇jam到野同唔係蚊之咁細聲既話<br />\n無論indoor定outdoor都係收得最清楚<br />\n壞處係你有3個人講野你就要3set<br />\n<br />\n記著<br />\n無論用咩mic 你唔夠聲然後俾勁大mic gain都係會好大ambiance<br />\n記得拍板／手 <br />\n<br />\n利申: Audio佬 唔識相機野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白，多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你意思係無論點錄都好，都係要後製整返落去，唔會直接入埋片？"},{"pid":"27ccc130735cfd9d43ac6d0df390e2e189ef7c62","tid":371881,"uid":36554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係買支gun, indoor買支pencil type既condenser都可以<br />\neg. rode ntg1, AKG c1000s etc.<br />\n好處係可以收幾個人講野同時唔太大ambiance<br />\n係咁意落個denoise都ok<br />\n壞處係outdoor好嘈既話ambiance都係會大 除非你拎著黎講<br />\n<br />\n一係買set wireless belt pack<br />\neg. sennheiser EW100, Shure SLX<br />\n好似買返黎有跟支mic<br />\n有錢想換咪可以諗<br />\ncountryman b3, Dpa 4060 etc.<br />\n鴨記咪霸mic pro係窮撚最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n好處係正確戴mic 冇jam到野同唔係蚊之咁細聲既話<br />\n無論indoor定outdoor都係